00:20:37.702 --> 00:20:39.964
these ideas and then obviously,
when I started working

00:20:39.964 --> 00:20:41.468
with my cousins, I started seeing the ...

00:20:41.468 --> 00:20:42.969
my cousins were motivated.

00:20:42.969 --> 00:20:44.967
They were, for the most
