00:20:47.105 --> 00:20:49.582
Nina: It's called Swiss-cheese learning.

00:20:49.582 --> 00:20:53.387
Swiss cheese learning (chuckles)
etc., and so, and very pragmatically,

00:20:53.387 --> 00:20:56.137
I started building these tools
and it's really a process

00:20:56.137 --> 00:20:57.062
of discovery.

00:20:57.062 --> 00:20:59.145
Teachers e-mailing me, saying,
