00:21:10.493 --> 00:21:13.177
"What are teachers telling me?"
and then it's kind of getting more

00:21:13.177 --> 00:21:14.574
and more traction.

00:21:14.574 --> 00:21:16.458
I started having people tell
me about a lot of this stuff.

00:21:16.458 --> 00:21:18.175
I mean, I knew a little bit
about the history before.

00:21:18.175 --> 00:21:22.760
I've heard about this whole
committee of 10 in 1890,

00:21:22.760 --> 00:21:24.389
somebody told me about
that in high school.

