00:33:27.515 --> 00:33:29.477
do you believe that all children can learn

00:33:29.477 --> 00:33:31.186
unless they have a serious disability?

00:33:31.186 --> 00:33:34.819
Can they all progress to the
levels that you have progressed to

00:33:34.819 --> 00:33:39.069
if they simply learn and master
and show an interest really

00:33:39.069 --> 00:33:43.081
in the subject matter
that they're studying?

