perhaps in how we are currently,

00:34:00.307 --> 00:34:02.897
trying to get the students
to learn these subjects?

00:34:02.897 --> 00:34:06.280
Sal: Yeah, so on the latter question,
if you asked me 20 years ago,

00:34:06.280 --> 00:34:09.059
