00:35:31.788 --> 00:35:35.558
pretty much everyone,
barring certain exceptions,

00:35:35.819 --> 00:35:37.062
we don't know where.

00:35:37.062 --> 00:35:37.809
I mean, we're still learning.

00:35:37.809 --> 00:35:39.078
We don't know but

00:35:39.078 --> 00:35:41.771
progress far ahead and we're
even seeing these classrooms.

00:35:42.355 --> 00:35:44.179
We traditionally think motivated kids,

00:35:44.179 --> 00:35:46.200
maybe that's 20% of kids but
