00:49:28.893 --> 00:49:31.060
Teachers have been telling
teachers and that's good

00:49:31.060 --> 00:49:33.730
because that way, these are
people who wanna make it work

00:49:33.730 --> 00:49:35.148
and they figured out and they tell us ways

00:49:35.148 --> 00:49:36.534
to make it work better.

00:49:36.534 --> 00:49:39.488
As soon as you make it top
down, I think it becomes,

00:49:41.780 --> 00:49:42.750
no one likes it anymore.

00:49:42.750 --> 00:49:44.607
And so, we want this
to be very grassroots.

00:49:44.607 --> 00:49:46.606
What I really tell people is
just tell people about it.

00:49:46.606 --> 00:49:48.506
Tell people, [tell them]
they have a free tutor.

00:49:48.506 --> 00:49:50.716
Tell teachers that look,
there might be another model

00:49:50.716 --> 00:49:52.437
that you probably will enjoy more.

00:49:52.437 --> 00:49:54.095
There are ways to reach more students

00:49:54.879 --> 00:49:57.906
and on top of that, and
